#1961
Between the planes~
You float, trapped between the planes of existence.  All around you
tendrils of mist turned red by the strange light caress you as you pass. 
There is no direction here, no landmarks, no matter that you can see other
than yourself, but you get a sense that you are not alone in this strange
place.  One way is as good as another, yet you feel that somewhere in this
place is a passage back to your own world, as well as a portal to the Abyss
itself.  
~
